# BKash Mobile Banking App UI

A modern and responsive BKash-inspired mobile banking interface built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This project showcases front-end development skills, responsive design principles, and clean UI implementation.

## Live Demo

🔗 https://shifajahmed.github.io/BKash-Mobile-Banking-App/

