## Features

* Responsive and Mobile-First Design
* Modern BKash-Inspired User Interface
* Interactive Components with JavaScript
* Clean and Maintainable Code Structure
* Optimized User Experience Across Devices

## Tech Stack

* HTML5
* Tailwind CSS
* JavaScript (ES6+)

## Project Purpose

This project was developed as a portfolio and learning project to demonstrate front-end development, responsive web design, and user interface implementation skills.

